681083,"uid":24730,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T18:04:03.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，笑咗。<br />\n飲大咗比人刻咗台灣喺額頭已經好笑，仲要比支那人打一身，真係醉爆伴郎團既情節"},{"pid":"76fa20498742c5d3ec86b6aca763d5e39365d95d","tid":681083,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T18:14:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27cf9a0739e65d26b43793074b7c149fcb79948f","tid":681083,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8b5ad5f089e03bc77156f4c019869caf509c544","tid":681083,"uid":24730,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T18:04:03.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，笑咗。<br />\n飲大咗比人刻咗台灣喺額頭已經好笑，仲要比支那人打一身，真係醉爆伴郎團既情節"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T18:16:51.000Z","msg":"Stu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尋日翻睇完"},{"pid":"2488d76e396f310aca6634a263f0d82fecf879c3","tid":681083,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T18:36:13.000Z","msg":"如果係美國人  已經係twitter 度開戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e56cbc458ac40655a837c5dc916dc94e9ee7f5","tid":681083,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T18:40:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171023/20191553 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171023%2F20191553%20&d=Zcr1ZrsZHQSr%2BmlG7wDQap4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=f5490d15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171023%2F20191553%20&h=ffe76aac\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171023/20191553 </a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171023/large/a1103a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171023%2Flarge%2Fa1103a.gif&h=4c83eb26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣上演《醉爆伴郎團》現實版，戲中男主角因酒醉紋身誤事，台灣一名外國人近日喝醉酒後，在額頭及下巴分別紋上「臺灣」兩字及台灣地圖，至酒醒後才嚇了一跳。他昨接受訪問時對事件深感後悔：「我老婆現在很生氣，我也不知該怎麼辦？」 <br />\n一名自稱紋身師父昨日在fb專頁《爆料公社》留言，指一名外國人額頭被刺「臺灣」兩字，據稱，老外在高雄喝醉走入紋身店，要求在額頭紋身，直至醒來後大嚇一跳，希望能清除紋身。事件引發掀然大波，有網民批評為老外紋身的店舖趁老外爛醉刺青，做法不妥。 <br />\n紋身師：對方堅持刺額頭 <br />\n涉事紋身師父韋丞接受訪問時表示，上周五凌晨，一名外國客人走進店內指自己很愛台灣，想在額頭刺「臺灣」，他從沒遇過要刺在臉上的客人，再三與對方確認。老外身上有酒味，但對答如流，當時還自己刮掉鬍子讓他刺青，「他刺青前很清醒，堅持要刺額頭的。」韋丞於是花約一小時完成額頭圖案、下巴則刺有綠色台灣圖騰。 <br />\n涉事老外昨表示，來台13年，因愛台灣右臂刺有台灣圖騰，接着他再指住額頭，「我是酒醉才刺這裏，我沒有酒醉的話，會刺身體其他部位。」「我那時喝醉了」、「我老婆現在很生氣」，他又指：「我現在不知該怎麼辦？」義大大昌醫院整外醫生黃昱豪指，可使用皮秒或淨膚雷射退色，預計要進行8到10次雷射治療，淡化五成紋身色素。"},{"pid":"043395b3fb064e8dd1a16add425308d564c6de58","tid":681083,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T01:14:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91618872935774293deaec246c4def5e1474917c","tid":681083,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:03:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f943cfd3c81c2cb20d8b1864852e33444784e2d2","tid":681083,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:04:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"460ff0571783695c305d1b901e5df1863b0c4ef6","tid":681083,"uid":179938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:10:13.000Z","msg":"贏國人笑到最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5332c941a7e4ef8c05d5aa4258324c4bbf6eb2a","tid":681083,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:11:47.000Z","msg":"垃圾無謂幾厲害都係垃圾 厲害了 垃圾國"}]}